          <li><a href="#product-1"><span class="toc-number">1</span>Tinctura de Propolis 30% Apicola Pasteurizata</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-2"><span class="toc-number">2</span>Tinctura de Propolis fara alcool Dacia Plant</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-3"><span class="toc-number">3</span>Spray de Gat Propolis si Miere Fares</a></li>
